        <h3 class="horton-blue bold" id="ref-e98ea9e6-e031-46ef-bde7-6680d0bdf153">Managing Hosts</h3>
        
          <p>Use Ambari Hosts to manage multiple HDP components such as DataNodes, NameNodes, TaskTrackers and
