        <h3 class="horton-blue bold" id="ref-50c9d54d-6862-497c-9e26-bdb3be3180e1">Collect Information</h3>
        
          <p>Before deploying an HDP cluster, you should collect the following information:</p>
          <ul class="bullet-list">
            
