                    <code>Configs</code>
                    <strong>.</strong>
                    In the Namenode section, look up the property
                    <strong>NameNode Directories</strong>
                    on your NameNode host.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    &lt;dfs.name.dir&gt;
                    <code>/current</code>
                  </p>
                  <aside class="custom-note">
                    <div class="icon"><img src="Icons/Note.png" width="50"></div>
