              </li>
              <li>
                <p>
                  <a href="#ref-6b596c1a-a195-4164-9368-6a60ef5abda5">Update all Agents</a>
                  - to point to the new Ambari Server.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p>
                  <a href="#ref-6fb36a70-54ef-4c39-9367-25a58968725d">Install the New Server</a>
