                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td rowspan="1">
                      <p>export CLUSTER_NAME=CLUSTER_NAME</p>
                    </td>
                    <td rowspan="1">
                      <p>Substitute the name of your cluster, set during the Ambari Install Wizard process. For
