                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td rowspan="1">
                      <p>export ADDITIONAL_NAMENODE_HOSTNAME=ANN_HOSTNAME</p>
                    </td>
                    <td rowspan="1">
                      <p>Substitute the FQDN of the host for the additional NameNode in your HA setup.</p>
