                  on the Ambari server to
                  <code>/usr/bin/</code>
                  on each failover host.
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p>Download
                  <code>hadoop.sh</code>
                  from
                  <code>/var/lib/ambari-server/resources/scripts</code>
